author: Matt H
title: Stage Stubs reviewed by Matt H
text:
Selling my tickets was a joy this year. The team were extremely helpful in helping me organise the seating charts for my wife bi-annual show. Hands down beats selling tickets for cash... never again!
Couldn't recommend more, great service and even better team
